text: KF Skënderbeu Poroj (, FK Skenderbeg Poroj) is a football club based in the village of Poroj, Tetovo, North Macedonia. They recently competed in the Macedonian Third League. ==History== The club was founded in 1993. ==References== ==External links== *Skënderbeu Poroj Facebook *Club info at MacedonianFootball *Football Federation of Macedonia Skenderbeu Poroj Skenderbeu Poroj Category:Association football clubs established in 1993 Category:1993 establishments in the Republic of Macedonia FK
